===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}
# {{lb|en|Scientology}} An [[extraterrestrial]] [[galactic]] leader said to have transported aliens to Earth 75 million years ago and murdered them with hydrogen bombs at sites of volcanoes, turning them into [[thetan]]s.
#* {{quote-book
|en
|year=1960s
|last=Hubbard
|first=L. Ron
|authorlink=L. Ron Hubbard
|title={{w|OT III}}: Wall of Fire
|url=https://archive.org/details/armstrong.4.documents/1995-01-23%20Armstrong%20Declaration/page/n3/
|archiveurl2=https://archive.ph/RSZKU
|archivedate2=12 January 2013
|url2=http://www.xenu.net/archive/OTIII-scholar/
|text=He caused people to be brought to<br>Teegeeack (Earth) and put an H Bomb<br>on the principal volcanoes (Incident 2)<br>and then the Pacific area ones<br>were taken in boxes to Hawaii<br>and the Atlantic Area ones to<br>Las Palmas and there "packaged."<br>His name was '''Xenu'''. He used<br>renegades.Various misleading<br>data by means of circuits etc.<br>were placed in the implants.}}
